2026-06-12T11:12:33.630282Z  INFO http.request{method=POST path=/api/v1/erp/init/initialize-with-db trace_id=62bd4f4464cd482e8222ca5b0bc71988 span_id=5d7b9de93556ab1c parent_span_id="" sampled=true}: sqlx::query: summary="INSERT INTO \"seaql_migrations\" (\"version\", …" db.statement="\n\nINSERT INTO \"seaql_migrations\" (\"version\", \"applied_at\") VALUES ($1, $2) RETURNING \"version\"\n" rows_affected=1 rows_returned=1 elapsed=54.892618ms elapsed_secs=0.054892618
